XML::RSS::Parser is a lightweight liberal OO parser of RSS feeds. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries: 
	XML::Parser 
	Class::XPath

